de.lmu.dbs.jforest.core
Class Dataset_old

java.lang.Object
  de.lmu.dbs.jforest.core.Dataset_old

public abstract class Dataset_old
extends java.lang.Object

Dataset base class. Supports basic sampling of samples. Samples can also be multi-dimensional, this just delivers the interface for Samplers.

Author:
Thomas Weber
